import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt


df = pd.read_csv("downloads/40k_balanced_pm_acl.csv").sample(frac=1)
df = df.dropna(subset=["labels"])
df["labels"] = df["labels"].astype(str)

df["text_length"] = df["text"].map(lambda t: len(t.split(" ")))
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
x1 = df.loc[df["labels"]=='1', 'text_length']
x2 = df.loc[df["labels"]=='0', 'text_length']


kwargs = dict(alpha=0.5, bins=200)

plt.hist(x1, **kwargs, color='g', label='positive')
plt.hist(x2, **kwargs, color='r', label='negative')
plt.gca().set(title='Sentence length', ylabel='Frequency')
plt.xlim(50,75)
plt.legend();
{% endraw %}
